{"tid":1267260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"相信七一係最後一次機會可以號召咁多人，我有小小嘢想講","createTime":"2019-06-29T19:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T05:28:57.000Z","uid":182575,"like":395,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"e88285f7c7236ab3e71b2a85621868387d0fc87c","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:17:56.000Z","msg":"香港人依家抗爭運動嘅模式唔同左<br />\n不撒不散提倡嘅「不散」普遍認為唔係死守/衝<br />\n而係持久be water 嘅不合作活動<br />\n利申我唔係話反對<br />\n不過事實係 可以堅持出嚟嘅人 一次比一次少<br />\n但人數卻從來都係抗爭嘅關鍵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">七一可能係最後一次機會可以聚集咁多人上街</span><br />\n<br />\n我好希望 呢次嘅遊行 再唔係行完就散嘅遊行<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人(假如仲有) 行到終點 留低吧<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人 一齊坐低 佔據港島<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逐步 一齊 決心 癱瘓香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我諗到如何將<span style=\"color: violet;\">和理非化到最大嘅效果</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">當然 歷史話我地知 單單咁樣係唔夠</span><br />\n但我相信香港人已經進化左 識得唔同嘅抗爭手法<br />\n之後故事發展會係點就要靠大家一齊想像<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但至少 肯留低嘅人夠多<br />\n先會有助同保護到想有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">其他行動</span>嘅手足</span>"},{"pid":"32b9b265f2ba178feee781541e3ddbccf5b74af7","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:21:19.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"dc0523ae6dece5e91c5c6f5be1b562b9d9f953e0","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d4d90f2404930f097d8897f494f34b3b91c70f","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:38:37.000Z","msg":"可能有人會驚變雨傘2.0<br />\n但我確信香港人係唔同左<br />\n我地要<span style=\"color: red;\">結合唔同方法</span>癱瘓香港<br />\n先有籌碼逼政府面對<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而留守係一個起點</span></span><br />\n係一個最多人接受 最易聚集人數嘅一步"},{"pid":"d3f5d4da7156ea201316e40d9f2d36eb1913361a","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:45:19.000Z","msg":"兄弟試下一齊各自爬山"},{"pid":"2a83340fe8db4d46105b20f1bc0635f002bd1bb7","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3f131ee17a707d0317c46ab36e731a8d2276f5","tid":1267260,"uid":91584,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:19:12.000Z","msg":"定唔好行曬全程<br />\n去到咁上下 全部人坐底唔行<br />\n銅鑼灣到金鐘就坐滿人"},{"pid":"6fa4d062f7a96dc9a91bc273b469addb00b42384","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"fa3f131ee17a707d0317c46ab36e731a8d2276f5","tid":1267260,"uid":91584,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:19:12.000Z","msg":"定唔好行曬全程<br />\n去到咁上下 全部人坐底唔行<br />\n銅鑼灣到金鐘就坐滿人"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:51:11.000Z","msg":"前線行到終點坐低<br />\n後來跟上嘅人塞住行唔到<br />\n就自然要沿路坐低了"},{"pid":"9b804b2b3b2a671f1ca218c0eca651a2d9f6131a","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c075bc11887d388699b8f79e9fc27a166ffad8e","tid":1267260,"uid":11374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"搵人係終點附近出入口 派下傳單 講下野<br />\n話比大家知依家選擇走 同 無出過黎分別不大<br />\nBla bla bla... 可能會吸納致部分人留底 <br />\n有無得諗"},{"pid":"cc963a4b1e3fd70cea95ee67b8288dff085e83e8","tid":1267260,"uid":182575,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"2c075bc11887d388699b8f79e9fc27a166ffad8e","tid":1267260,"uid":11374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"搵人係終點附近出入口 派下傳單 講下野<br />\n話比大家知依家選擇走 同 無出過黎分別不大<br />\nBla bla bla... 可能會吸納致部分人留底 <br />\n有無得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"都可以<br />\n最緊要唔好比民陣水到啲人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999293fa5aad0d1adb21209899b374390a